@Lost00 @EZ_DUZ_IT nothing wrong with a good speculation, people liken it to gambling, but from my point of view, they are not the same.  

When we first invested in $AAOI at $7-8 a share, for example, my ppl thought it was gambling. It was a spec that. has turned into an investment, with profitability and massive growth. But there was none of that in 2024, it was an idea based on the demand picture we were seeing on the ground in Texas DCs.   

$NAK could become a great investment, but for now its still a speculation, one we like and feel is well worth the risk of losing our capital, should the mine not open in the next decade or so.

